Feasibility and validity of a tool for identification of people with 
intellectual disabilities in need of palliative care (PALLI).

Vrijmoeth C(1), Groot CM(2), Christians MGM(3), Assendelft WJJ(4), Festen 
DAM(5), van der Rijt CCD(6), van Schrojenstein Lantman-de Valk HMJ(7), Vissers 
