Restricted Presence of POU6F2 in Human Corneal Endothelial Cells Uncovered by 
Extension of the Promoter-level Expression Atlas.

Yoshihara M(1), Hara S(2), Tsujikawa M(3), Kawasaki S(4), Hayashizaki Y(5), Itoh 
